          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Another celebrity ring that drew attention was Megan Fox’s <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/engagement-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"engagement ring,\">engagement ring,</a> which featured an emerald and a diamond set together.</p><p>The stones were arranged so they appeared to lean toward each other, symbolising two individuals coming together. This ring design reinforced the romantic meaning behind Toi et Moi rings.</p><p>The use of different gemstones made the ring feel bold and personal.</p><p>Lucira’s Emerald & Round Cut Diamond Toi et Moi Ring reflects a similar concept, where contrasting shapes and stones create visual balance.</p>",
