            "content": "<p>Model and actress Emily Ratajkowski also popularised the Toi et Moi trend with her engagement ring.</p><p>Her ring featured two diamonds of different shapes - a princess-cut diamond and a pear-shaped diamond placed side by side.</p><p>The contrast between the shapes gave the ring a modern and artistic feel.</p><p>This idea of pairing two unique diamond shapes can also be seen in designs like the Pear & Radiant Cut Diamond <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/toi-et-moi-rings\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Toi et Moi Ring\">Toi et Moi Ring</a>, where two different cuts complement each other beautifully.</p>",
